WEBVTT

00:02:28.934 --> 00:02:30.711
from the funeral industry.

00:02:31.820 --> 00:02:33.985
It's a multi-billion-dollar industry,

00:02:34.009 --> 00:02:36.993
and its economic model
is based on the principle

00:02:37.017 --> 00:02:42.496
of protection, sanitation
and beautification of the corpse.

00:02:43.610 --> 00:02:45.782
Whether they mean to or not,

00:02:45.806 --> 00:02:50.299
the funeral industry promotes
this idea of human exceptionalism.

00:02:50.816 --> 00:02:52.458
It doesn't matter what it takes,

00:02:52.482 --> 00:02:53.774
how much it costs,

00:02:53.798 --> 00:02:55.756
how bad it is for the environment,

00:02:55.780 --> 00:02:59.053
we're going to do it
because humans are worth it!

